  <brief_title>A Research Study of Zoledronic Acid in Children and Adolescents With Osteoporosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled Efficacy and Safety Trial of Intravenous (i.v.) Zoledronic Acid Twice Yearly Compared to Placebo in Osteoporotic Children Treated With Glucocorticoids</official_title>
  <sponsors>
